OL,3,CNew Chief Executive appointed for NHS
OL,4,CBorders
OL,6,FPeter Moore has been appointed as
OL,7,FChief Executive for NHS Borders
OL,8,Ffollowing the retirement of Ralph
OL,9,FRoberts.
OL,11,FMr Moore is set to take on the role in
OL,12,FSeptember and joins NHS Borders from
OL,13,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care where he
OL,14,Fworked as Director of System
OL,15,FImprovement.
OL,17,FChair of NHS Borders Karen Hamilton
OL,18,Fsaid: "I look forward to welcoming
OL,19,FPeter to the board.
