OL,6,F"The challenges facing NHS Borders are
OL,7,Fwell documented and Peter is well
OL,8,Fplaced to lead the organisation
OL,9,Fthrough them as we look to ensure our
OL,10,Fservices are transformed so that they
OL,11,Fare sustainable and meet the future
OL,12,Fneeds of our communities.
OL,14,F"At the same time I wish to place on
OL,15,Frecord my thanks and best wishes to
OL,16,FRalph for a well deserved, happy and
OL,17,Ffulfilling retirement."
