OL,3,CNew Chief Executive appointed for NHS
OL,4,CBorders
OL,6,FCommenting on his appointment Peter
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is a genuine privilege to be
OL,8,Fjoining NHS Borders as Chief
OL,9,FExecutive. I am really looking forward
OL,10,Fto working alongside the board's
OL,11,Fdedicated and compassionate staff to
OL,12,Fhelp deliver the best care possible
OL,13,Ffor our patients.
OL,15,F"We will no doubt face significant
OL,16,Fchallenges, but I am confident that we
OL,17,Fwill face these together with our
OL,18,Fpartners, and in doing so will be able
OL,19,Fto provide the best support we can to
OL,20,Fthe communities we serve."
